    "And these are the generations of <span class=\"person\">Isaac</span>, <span class=\"person\">Abraham</span>'s son: <span class=\"person\">Abraham</span> begat <span class=\"person\">Isaac</span>:",
    "And <span class=\"person\">Isaac</span> was forty years old when he took <span class=\"person\">Rebekah</span> to wife, the daughter of <span class=\"person\">Bethuel</span> the Syrian of <span class=\"place\">Padanaram</span>, the sister to <span class=\"person\">Laban</span> the Syrian.",
