    "And <span class=\"person\">Jacob</span> went near unto <span class=\"person\">Isaac</span> his father; and he felt him, and said, The voice is <span class=\"person\">Jacob</span>'s voice, but the hands are the hands of <span class=\"person\">Esau</span>.",
