    "And God said unto <span class=\"person\">Jacob</span>, Arise, go up to <span class=\"place\">Bethel</span>, and dwell there: and make there an altar unto God, that appeared unto thee when thou fleddest from the face of <span class=\"person\">Esau</span> thy brother.",
