    "Now these are the generations of <span class=\"person\">Esau</span>, who is <span class=\"person\">Edom</span>.",
    "<span class=\"person\">Esau</span> took his wives of the daughters of <span class=\"place\">Canaan</span>; <span class=\"person\">Adah</span> the daughter of <span class=\"person\">Elon</span> the Hittite, and <span class=\"person\">Aholibamah</span> the daughter of <span class=\"person\">Anah</span> the daughter of <span class=\"person\">Zibeon</span> the Hivite;",
