    "Duke <span class=\"person\">Dishon</span>, duke <span class=\"person\">Ezer</span>, duke <span class=\"person\">Dishan</span>: these are the dukes that came of <span class=\"person\">Hori</span>, among their dukes in the land of <span class=\"place\">Seir</span>.",
